{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The legend says Newton dreamed of apples... A lot!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419790/extras/Newton_Steam_Sleep_V01.gif?t=1739891817\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Newton</strong> is a solo 2D <i>pixel art</i>\u00a0arcade-<strong><i>platformer</i></strong> game made with Unreal Engine 5. Collect apples, master gravity and set high score in this simple but challenging adventure!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Master Unique Powers</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Invert gravity.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grab the teleportation apple.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Teleport instantly to the next spot! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419790/extras/Newton_Teleportation.gif?t=1739891817\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Become the Best Challenger</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Train and <strong>improve</strong> locally, beat the high scores, and become the top player on the online leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419790/extras/Newton_Steam_Leaderboard_En.png?t=1739891817\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unlock the Codex</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover the good, the bad, and the quirky apples:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the hidden apples.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn each apple\u2019s unique properties.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Check your personal counter.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master all their secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/34